5. Move to the countertops near the sink.

9. Open the cabinet door.

20. Open the cabinet or pantry door.
21. Place the box of cereal inside the cabinet or pantry.
22. Close the cabinet or pantry door.
23. Pick up the two cups from the countertops on each side of the sink.
